SELECT Athletes.name, Workouts.workout_name, AthleteWorkoutHistory.completed_date FROM Athletes JOIN AthleteWorkoutHistory ON Athletes.athlete_id = AthleteWorkoutHistory.athlete_id JOIN Workouts ON Workouts.workout_id = AthleteWorkoutHistory.workout_id WHERE Athletes.age <= 30 ORDER BY AthleteWorkoutHistory.completed_date DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT AthleteFitnessData.athlete_id, FitnessLevels.level_name, AthleteFitnessData.weight_progress FROM AthleteFitnessData JOIN FitnessLevels ON AthleteFitnessData.level_id = FitnessLevels.level_id WHERE AthleteFitnessData.weight_progress > 0.5;

SELECT Athletes.name AS Athlete_Name, Workouts.workout_name AS Workout_Name, AthleteWorkoutHistory.completed_date AS Date_Completed FROM Athletes JOIN AthleteWorkoutHistory ON Athletes.athlete_id = AthleteWorkoutHistory.athlete_id JOIN Workouts ON Workouts.workout_id = AthleteWorkoutHistory.workout_id WHERE Athletes.height > 170 AND AthleteWorkoutHistory.completed_date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY AthleteWorkoutHistory.completed_date ASC LIMIT 5;
